’Щ@3da773c759876227ea651c1c0d2865ae887f098f223d0d306c81cf2678515fddЩ Title: title: from json
Path: Flags
Content:
``--objects, -o``
: Treat each line as a separate value.
``--strict, -s``
: Follow the json specification exactly.
